        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme “P1, P2, P3, P4, SIV, Guided Flying” is implemented by the Uttarakhand Tourism Development Board under the Department of Tourism, Government of Uttarakhand. The scheme aims to develop skilled and certified paragliding professionals from Uttarakhand who can work as Tandem Pilots, Instructors, or Competitors in the tourism sector.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "**Beneficiaries can work in firms operating as:**\n\n- Tandem Pilots\n- Instructors\n- Competitors\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The aim of the scheme is to train and develop skilled youth of Uttarakhand, aged between 18 to 30 years, who are educated, mentally, and physically fit, to become professional paragliding pilots and instructors.",
